#: tvisabout.caption
msgctxt "tvisabout.caption"
msgid "About"
msgstr "关于"

#: tvisabout.label_description.caption
msgid "OpenRSAT is an open-source, cross-platform tool for Active Directory administration via an interface, inspired by Microsoft’s RSAT tools. It enables system administrators to manage users, groups, and organizational units on Windows, Linux, and macOS. "
msgstr "OpenRSAT 是一个开源、跨平台的 Active Directory 图形化管理工具，灵感来自 Microsoft RSAT 工具。它可以帮助系统管理员在 Windows、Linux 和 macOS 上管理用户、组和组织单位。"

#: tvisabout.label_discord.caption
msgid "Click to join Tranquil IT discord."
msgstr "点击加入 Tranquil IT Discord。"

#: tvisabout.label_documentation.caption
msgid "Click to open Documentation page. (Not yet implemented)"
msgstr "点击打开文档页面。（尚未实现）"

#: tvisabout.label_github.caption
msgid "Click to open OpenRSAT github page."
msgstr "点击打开 OpenRSAT GitHub 页面。"

#: tvisabout.label_githubissue.caption
msgid "You found a bug or want to give feedback? Click to open an issue on github!"
msgstr "发现问题或想反馈？点击在 GitHub 上创建 issue！"

#: tvisabout.label_tranquilit.caption
msgid "Click to open Tranquil IT home page."
msgstr "点击打开 Tranquil IT 主页。"

#: tvisabout.label_waptpackage.caption
msgid "Click to open OpenRSAT WAPT package."
msgstr "点击打开 OpenRSAT WAPT 包页面。"

